2002-1802 (La. 10/14/02)

CERTIFIED FINANCE, INC. v. Rebecca CUNARD, A. Gill Dyer, Hillary Thomas Murphy and an Unnamed Partnership/Joint Venture Composed of Rebecca A. Cunard, A. Gill Dyer and Hillary Thomas Murphy. No. 2002-C-1802. Supreme Court of Louisiana. Oct. 14, 2002.

In re Cunard, Rebecca et al.; — Defendant; Applying for Writ of Certiorari and/or Review, Parish of E. Baton Rouge, 19th Judicial District Court Div. M, No. 473,853; to the Court of Appeal, First Circuit, No. 2001 CA 0797.

Denied.

JOHNSON, J., would grant the writ.
